commit.message: Removed slide methods from artist and album, condensed populateCurrentSong()
Polyfilled Promise and fetch for IE, changed queue elements from span to p
jQuery no longer needed, now linting js with webpack, previous commit changed control icons to use material icon font
Cleaned up css and switched to scss, implemented webpack, locally hosting google font
Cleaned up and added some logging
Changed the player from my multithreaded approach to use vlc Events instead. Seems to work much better
got rid of readme md extension
Added some todo's to the readme
Moved all the functions that were in the routes to controller files
Setup player so that it shuts down a worker thread before starting a new one
Split Player into a QueueListener and Player class. Had QueueListener stop a playing thread if a new song is requested while another thread is running.
Changed send-test.py so that it can accept args from the command line. Added some comments and print output to player.py
